OL,5,Ctaken ill
OL,7,FCrystal Palace manager Roy Hodgson is
OL,8,Fin a stable condition and having tests
OL,9,Fin hospital after being taken ill
OL,10,Fduring training on Thursday, the
OL,11,FPremier League club have confirmed.
OL,13,FThe 76-year-old was due to speak at a
OL,14,Fscheduled press conference at 1.30pm
OL,15,Fto preview Monday's Premier League
OL,16,Fgame against Everton, but members of
OL,17,Fthe media waiting outside the club's
OL,18,FNew Beckenham training ground were
OL,19,Finformed the briefing would not take
OL,20,Fplace.
