OL,3,CPalace boss Roy Hodgson in stable
OL,4,Ccondition in hospital after being
OL,5,Ctaken ill
OL,7,FAccording to reports, Palace are set
OL,8,Fto sack Hodgson, with ex-Eintracht
OL,9,FFrankfurt boss Oliver Glasner a strong
OL,10,Ffavourite to take the job.
OL,12,FAn update from the club later on
OL,13,FThursday read: "Following news that
OL,14,FRoy Hodgson was taken ill during
OL,15,Ftoday's training session, we can
OL,16,Fconfirm that he is now stable and is
OL,17,Fcurrently undergoing tests in hospital.
OL,19,F"Everybody at the club sends their
OL,20,Fbest wishes to Roy for a speedy
OL,21,Frecovery."
